trailingComments.value:
*
     * Get the textual name for a log level.
     *
     * @param {number} logLevel The log level to get a textual name for.
     * @returns {string}
     *
     * @example
     * const infoText = LOGLEVEL.getTextualNameForLogLevel(LOGLEVEL.INFO);
     * // infoText === 'INFO'
